column4:
Hello info,

Good day!

This memo is to confirm our intention to increase your basic salary 
wages as per the attach payroll computation. The increase will take 
effect from this  month of August  2024 and will be reflected in your 
pay at the end of the month. To indicate acceptance, Kindly Check the 
below attach document to review the monthly activity statement and 
computation of all the employee's approved for the increament of salary.


NB: This document is confidential and should not be forwarded. For 
issues with accessing document, kindly reach out to the HR Manager


Regards,


HR Manager
